# MDF-7 fixture: root-level .rsync-filter
# Exercises: blank lines, comments, basic include/exclude prefix rules.
# This file is loaded by every receiver that walks the source tree with
# the canonical dir-merge /.rsync-filter invocation.

# Blank lines and comments should be ignored.

# Always exclude the canonical "always-exclude.txt" sanity file.
- always-exclude.txt

# Always include the canonical "always-include.txt" sanity file.
+ always-include.txt
